DESCRIPTION_ACTIONLOG: Logs guild actions in a specific channel specified
DESCRIPTION_AFK: Let people know you are AFK when they mention you
DESCRIPTION_ALIASES_SHOW: Show value of a specific alias
DESCRIPTION_ALIASES_USERARGS: Set flag true or false in order to include user arguments as part of command
DESCRIPTION_BIGTEXTD: Same as bigtext, but I also remove your command
DESCRIPTION_CLEAN: I will delete my messages from the last 100 messages
DESCRIPTION_LENNYD: Same as lenny, but I also remove your command
DESCRIPTION_PERMISSIONS_LIST: Display a list of all available permissions
DESCRIPTION_PERMISSIONS_MEMBER_CHANNEL: Permissions for user in a specific channel
DESCRIPTION_PERMISSIONS_ROLE_CHANNEL: Permissions for a role in a specific channel
DESCRIPTION_PRO_ADD: Adds a manual subscription. Expires can be never if you give value -1 for it
DESCRIPTION_PRO_CHECK: Shows if this server has Ayana PRO or not and who upgraded it
DESCRIPTION_PRO_DOWNGRADE: Downgrades this server or the one specified with the ID from Ayana PRO
DESCRIPTION_PRO_KEYS: Handle key add, generate, get and remove
DESCRIPTION_PRO_LEAVEGUILD: Determines what guilds are no longer pro and prompts if they should be left
DESCRIPTION_PRO_STATUS: Shows your running Ayana PRO subscriptions and upgrade count
DESCRIPTION_PRO_UPGRADE: Upgrades this server to Ayana PRO
DESCRIPTION_RANDOM: Display a random no with support of upper and lower limit
DESCRIPTION_ROLEMEMBERS: List the members of a role
DESCRIPTION_SAYD: Same as say, but I also remove your command
DESCRIPTION_SHRUGD: Same as shrug, but I also remove your command
DESCRIPTION_SPONGEBOB: Spongebob mocking meme; also memes the text you give
DESCRIPTION_SUPPORT: Display invite link for support channel
DESCRIPTION_URBAN: Looks up a word on urbandictionary.com
